name: Catch the Temmie (Beta_v0.2.1)
description:
In this game you need to catch a temmie that is movin around the room, each time you click the temmie you earn points.

If you have any idea for the game feel free to leave it in the discussion board, remember that this is a Beta and it's up to changes.
